---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms & Conditions">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <header class="legal-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-section-heading">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
        <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="legal-body">
        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using this website (<strong>aurearresidences.com</strong>, the "Site"),
            you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please
            discontinue use of the Site immediately.
          </p>
          <p>
            These terms apply to all visitors, enquirers, and any person who submits information
            through the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. About Aurea Residences</h2>
          <p>
            Aurea Residences is a residential development marketed by Aurea Development Group ("we",
            "us", "our"). The Site is a marketing and information resource. It does not constitute a
            legal offer, contract, or reservation of any unit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. Accuracy of Information</h2>
          <p>
            All imagery, floor plans, specifications, pricing, and availability information on this
            Site are indicative and subject to change without notice. Computer-generated images
            (CGIs) and renders are for illustrative purposes only and may not precisely represent
            the finished development.
          </p>
          <p>
            We make no warranty, express or implied, as to the accuracy, completeness, or
            suitability of any information on the Site for any particular purpose.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. No Offer or Advice</h2>
          <p>
            Nothing on this Site constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. You should
            seek independent professional advice before making any property acquisition decision.
            Aurea Residences does not hold or offer financial advice in any jurisdiction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Enquiries and Communications</h2>
          <p>
            When you submit an enquiry, schedule a viewing, or otherwise contact us through the
            Site, you consent to being contacted by our sales team via email, telephone, or other
            means you have provided. You may withdraw this consent at any time by contacting us at
            the details below.
          </p>
          <p>
            Submitting an enquiry creates no obligation on either party and does not constitute a
            reservation or agreement to purchase.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this Site — including text, photography, renders, branding, logos, and
            code — is owned by or licensed to Aurea Development Group. You may not reproduce,
            distribute, or create derivative works from any material on this Site without prior
            written consent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            This Site uses cookies and similar technologies to improve your browsing experience,
            analyse traffic, and support our marketing. By continuing to use the Site, you consent
            to our use of cookies as described in our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            You may manage or disable cookies through your browser settings at any time. Disabling
            certain cookies may affect the functionality of the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>8. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            The Site may contain links to third-party websites for your convenience. We have no
            control over the content or practices of those sites and accept no responsibility for
            them. Their inclusion does not imply endorsement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Aurea Development Group shall not be
            liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential loss arising from your use
            of or reliance on this Site or its content.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with applicable law. Any dispute
            arising from your use of this Site shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the
            courts of the relevant territory.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>11. Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Site after any changes
            constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms. We recommend reviewing this page
            periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>12. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any questions regarding these Terms, please contact us at <a
              href="mailto:legal@aurearresidences.com">legal@aurearresidences.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="link-underline legal-back">Return home</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap {
    max-width: 48rem;
    padding: 0 var(--space-edge);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .legal-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-meta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-black) 40%, transparent);
  }

  .legal-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-black) 65%, transparent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-black);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .legal-back {
    display: inline-block;
  }
</style>
